commit_message:
Update for packaging JavaDoc and sources

- Make Maven generate JavaDoc and source archive when packaging
- Fix errors in JavaDoc (ignore warning for now)
previous_commit_message:
Update Travis CI configuration

- Set the max stack size to unlimited
